msgid "# Export-HgsServerState"
msgstr "# Export-HgsServerState"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid ""
"Exports the local Host Guardian Service instance's state to enable recovery "
"scenarios."
msgstr "导出本地Host Guardian服务实例的状态信息，以便在需要恢复的情况下使用这些数据。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The **Export-HgsServer** cmdlet exports the Host Guardian Service (HGS) "
"state to enable recovery scenarios."
msgstr ""
"`Export-HgsServer` cmdlet 可以导出 Host Guardian Service (HGS) 的状态信息，以便用于恢复相关场景。"

msgid ""
"The cmdlet causes the following Host Guardian Service state to be exported "
"to the specified output file:"
msgstr "此 cmdlet 会导致以下 Host Guardian Service 状态被导出到指定的输出文件中："

msgid ""
"For more information about the scenario terms, see [Security and "
"Assurance](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=699209)."
msgstr ""
"有关场景术语的更多信息，请参阅[安全与保障](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=699209)。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Export HGS server state and protect it with a password"
msgstr "### 示例 1：导出 HGS 服务器的状态，并用密码进行保护"

msgid ""
"This command exports the HGS server state and protects the exported state using a password.\n"
"The exported state is stored at the file specified by the **Path** parameter."
msgstr "该命令用于导出HGS服务器的状态，并使用密码对导出的状态进行保护。导出的状态将被存储在由**Path**参数指定的文件中。"

msgid ""
"Use the **ConvertTo-SecureString** cmdlet to generate a secure string that "
"represents the password."
msgstr "使用 `ConvertTo-SecureString` cmdlet 生成一个表示密码的安全字符串。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid "Forces the command to run without asking for user confirmation."
msgstr "强制命令运行，而无需请求用户确认。"

msgid "Specifies the password with which to encrypt the keys."
msgstr "指定用于加密密钥的密码。"

msgid "Specifies the path for the exported file."
msgstr "指定导出文件的路径。"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行cmdlet之前会提示您进行确认。"

msgid ""
"Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs.\n"
"The cmdlet is not run."
msgstr "展示了如果运行该cmdlet会发生什么情况。但实际上并没有运行该cmdlet。"

msgid "### CommonParameters"
msgstr "### CommonParameters"

msgid ""
"This cmdlet supports the common parameters: -Debug, -ErrorAction, "
"-ErrorVariable, -InformationAction, -InformationVariable, -OutVariable, "
"-OutBuffer, -PipelineVariable, -Verbose, -WarningAction, and "
"-WarningVariable. For more information, see about_CommonParameters "
"(http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113216)."
msgstr ""
"此 cmdlet "
"支持以下常见参数：-Debug、-ErrorAction、-ErrorVariable、-InformationAction、-OutputVariable、-OutBuffer、-PipelineVariable、-Verbose、-WarningAction"
" 和 -WarningVariable。有关更多信息，请参阅 about_CommonParameters "
"(http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113216)。"

